title: Easy Zucchini Noodle Alfredo
directions: Use a spiralizer or vegetable peeler to made zucchini noodles.(I have Vegetti and Paderno spiralizers. See links below.)
Heat olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.
Add zucchini noodles to pan and saute for about 5 minutes.
Add cream cheese, sour cream and Parmesan cheese to pan and stir to combine.
Pour sauce over noodles and toss to combine.
Top with additional Parmesan cheese, if desired.
ingredients: 1.5 ounces of cream cheese, room temperature
